
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:15,360
"Ashes of Love"



00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:17,240
"Episode 33"



00:02:18,260 --> 00:02:19,700
Dad, what are you going to do?



00:02:20,140 --> 00:02:22,420
Sui, you may be accidentally injured.



00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:23,880
Come over here.



00:02:50,200 --> 00:02:50,860
Sui.



00:02:51,880 --> 00:02:52,600
Why are you



00:02:52,810 --> 00:02:54,800
so obsessive with someone



00:02:54,980 --> 00:02:56,680
who doesn’t love you?



00:02:58,540 --> 00:03:00,220
If he really cared about you,



00:03:00,720 --> 00:03:01,960
he would have married you.



00:03:08,700 --> 00:03:11,060
Ask them to step back or I won’t come there.



00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:17,000
Step back.



00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:24,600
Come here.



00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:26,840
Come to me.



00:04:11,420 --> 00:04:13,740
King Yi, see?



00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:18,720
My daughter is…



00:04:35,280 --> 00:04:36,080
Sui.



00:04:37,860 --> 00:04:38,620
Dad,



00:04:40,620 --> 00:04:42,460
you were nice to me this life.



00:04:44,320 --> 00:04:45,520
I’ll keep it in mind.



00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:50,400
You’re a good dad,



00:04:53,780 --> 00:04:54,800
but it is a pity that



00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:58,220
compared with Xu Feng,



00:05:00,540 --> 00:05:01,540
you’re nothing



00:05:03,840 --> 00:05:06,280
but a mere mortal.



00:05:15,660 --> 00:05:16,320
My Lord.



00:05:17,740 --> 00:05:18,320
My Lord.



00:05:21,540 --> 00:05:23,100
Sui. Sui.



00:05:24,280 --> 00:05:24,960
My Lord.



00:05:25,340 --> 00:05:26,020
My Lord.



00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:32,780
My Lord. My Lord.



00:05:38,880 --> 00:05:40,240
Listen up,
everyone from Duke Nanping Mansion,



00:05:40,620 --> 00:05:42,040
if you put down your weapons right now



00:05:42,340 --> 00:05:43,800
and fight a battle following His Majesty,



00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:45,470
you can expiate your crime by good deeds



00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:47,320
and won’t be punished



00:05:47,340 --> 00:05:48,440
for assassinating His Majesty.



00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:50,920
Or your nine clans will be killed.



00:05:51,640 --> 00:05:53,420
I didn’t know



00:05:53,420 --> 00:05:54,820
my dad would commit regicide.



00:05:55,820 --> 00:05:56,620
I…



00:05:58,940 --> 00:05:59,680
I…



00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:35,020
You have just repelled the army of Liangguo.



00:06:35,020 --> 00:06:36,080
Would you like to
rest for a night before you leave?



00:06:36,540 --> 00:06:37,360
Cousin.



00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:39,360
Go.



00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:47,960
Cousin.



00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:51,720
My dad is dead.



00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:57,020
Now I can only depend on you.



00:06:58,600 --> 00:06:59,260
I know.



00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:02,200
I’ll keep what you did for Huaiwu



00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,760
in my mind.



00:07:04,300 --> 00:07:05,500
If you meet any problems in the future,



00:07:06,100 --> 00:07:07,500
I won’t stand idly by.



00:07:08,140 --> 00:07:09,660
I have only one problem,



00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:17,100
that is, I want you to marry me willingly.



00:07:18,860 --> 00:07:21,140
Do you still mind the affair
between Lord Puchi and me?



00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,700
That was a mistake.



00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:26,800
My love for you is so true.



00:07:26,960 --> 00:07:29,040
I’ll marry no one but you this life.



00:07:29,520 --> 00:07:30,160
Sui He.



00:07:31,790 --> 00:07:33,120
Life is vain and
I’m just a passerby in the world.



00:07:33,400 --> 00:07:34,540
If you don’t promise me,



00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:37,000
I don’t want to live anymore.



00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:43,900
Sui He,



00:07:45,460 --> 00:07:46,840
I love someone



00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:49,780
and can’t love others.



00:07:51,260 --> 00:07:52,300
So from today on,



00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:55,320
I’ll treat you as my real sister.



00:07:57,100 --> 00:07:58,600
Do you love



00:08:01,320 --> 00:08:02,280
Jin Mi?



00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:04,640
Yes.



00:08:07,020 --> 00:08:08,100
Why?



00:08:09,140 --> 00:08:10,720
She’s Saint Girl of Saint Doctors’ Family.



00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:12,560
It’s impossible for you to marry her.



00:08:13,220 --> 00:08:13,920
Cousin.



00:08:14,840 --> 00:08:16,380
I fell in love with you since I was a child.



00:08:17,260 --> 00:08:18,680
I have done so much for you.



00:08:19,620 --> 00:08:20,660
I even killed dad…



00:08:22,660 --> 00:08:25,140
Why are you so cruel to me?



00:08:25,620 --> 00:08:26,500
Sui He.



00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:28,900
I know your mind.



00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,380
I’m grateful for



00:08:31,940 --> 00:08:33,200
what you’ve done for me,



00:08:34,659 --> 00:08:35,679
but



00:08:38,340 --> 00:08:40,039
it has also terrified me.



00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:42,600
I know I’m unable to repay your kindness.



00:08:43,460 --> 00:08:44,340
If you’re in danger



00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:46,100
in the future,



00:08:46,100 --> 00:08:47,040
I’ll protect you with my life.



00:08:47,760 --> 00:08:49,040
But I can by no means



00:08:50,620 --> 00:08:52,020
marry you.



00:08:57,940 --> 00:08:58,620
Cousin,



00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:01,380
what I have done is all for you.



00:09:01,760 --> 00:09:03,800
What’s special about Jin Mi?



00:09:04,640 --> 00:09:07,380
You chase her both in heaven and earth.



00:09:07,380 --> 00:09:08,140
Sui He.



00:09:12,020 --> 00:09:13,860
You’re unstable after
so many things happened in these days.



00:09:15,040 --> 00:09:16,180
Let’s talk about it another day.



00:09:20,940 --> 00:09:22,080
Why haven’t you taken off
your amour yet, Your Majesty?



00:09:22,380 --> 00:09:23,260
Is the horse ready?



00:09:23,260 --> 00:09:24,060
Yes.



00:09:24,060 --> 00:09:25,060
I chose a team of elite soldiers



00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:26,320
to escort you to the Villa.



00:09:26,460 --> 00:09:27,460
Send Princess back.



00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:35,400
Jin Mi, I won’t let you get what you want.



00:10:12,380 --> 00:10:13,120
Your Majesty.



00:10:16,920 --> 00:10:18,580
Am I dreaming again?



00:10:19,580 --> 00:10:20,580
No.



00:10:27,980 --> 00:10:28,860
You’re back.



00:10:30,440 --> 00:10:31,880
I wanted to see you earlier.



00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,140
What’s wrong with you?



00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:36,400
Qiang Huo said you got inflamed.



00:10:37,040 --> 00:10:37,780
You know



00:10:37,920 --> 00:10:39,360
I never believe in her medical skill.



00:10:40,420 --> 00:10:42,440
Moreover, you’re so weak now.



00:10:42,760 --> 00:10:44,280
I don’t believe you just got inflamed.



00:10:45,580 --> 00:10:46,920
Is it that you’re poisoned



00:10:46,920 --> 00:10:48,920
when you study those strange herbs?



00:10:51,140 --> 00:10:55,180
Jin Mi, you know your symptoms best.



00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:58,020
Tell me what happened to you.



00:10:58,840 --> 00:10:59,620
Your Majesty,



00:11:00,800 --> 00:11:02,800
although Qiang Huo is not as skilled as me,



00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:05,380
she is a member of
Saint Doctors’ Family after all.



00:11:05,820 --> 00:11:06,880
I did



00:11:07,480 --> 00:11:08,600
get inflamed.



00:11:09,840 --> 00:11:10,960
How come



00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:12,160
you’re so weak



00:11:12,160 --> 00:11:13,440
and coughed so badly?



00:11:14,180 --> 00:11:15,440
I don’t know much about medicine,



00:11:16,040 --> 00:11:17,120
but you can’t lie to me.



00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:20,200
How dare I lie to you?



00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:22,200
I actually



00:11:23,260 --> 00:11:26,360
have been prone to get inflamed
since I was a child.



00:11:26,620 --> 00:11:28,560
I may go faint after eating just one litchi,



00:11:29,040 --> 00:11:30,740
but I’m good at pharmacy,



00:11:31,040 --> 00:11:32,740
so I have developed



00:11:33,100 --> 00:11:34,100
a kind of medicine



00:11:34,420 --> 00:11:35,900
to cure this symptom once and for all.



00:11:36,580 --> 00:11:38,940
I just wanted to try it out,



00:11:39,420 --> 00:11:40,580
so I ate some longans.



00:11:40,740 --> 00:11:43,240
Unexpectedly, I passed out at once.



00:11:43,600 --> 00:11:44,860
That’s embarrassing.



00:11:45,140 --> 00:11:46,100
Where is the medicine?



00:11:56,540 --> 00:11:57,520
How many tablets should you take?



00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:03,820
Three ones.



00:12:11,620 --> 00:12:12,740
Take them.



00:12:36,220 --> 00:12:38,360
Lie down and have a good rest.



00:12:41,760 --> 00:12:44,640
Your Majesty, I didn’t lie to you, right?



00:12:46,020 --> 00:12:47,060
After taking the medicine,



00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:48,640
I feel much better now.



00:12:49,220 --> 00:12:50,480
I’m all right.



00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:51,760
How about



00:12:52,800 --> 00:12:54,820
taking a walk in the courtyard



00:12:55,120 --> 00:12:57,700
or playing chess with you?



00:12:58,300 --> 00:12:59,440
Promise me



00:12:59,980 --> 00:13:01,660
you can’t scare me like that again.



00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:08,860
Your Majesty,



00:13:09,520 --> 00:13:11,280
did you return from the battlefield directly?



00:13:13,020 --> 00:13:14,100
So what?



00:13:17,020 --> 00:13:19,580
I just heard that you’re God of War before,



00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:21,180
but I have never



00:13:21,820 --> 00:13:23,620
seen you in martial attire.



00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:26,920
They’re right.



00:13:28,120 --> 00:13:29,140
You look handsome.



00:13:54,520 --> 00:13:56,700
Princess Sui He, what can I do for you?



00:13:58,120 --> 00:13:59,120
Send this letter



00:13:59,320 --> 00:14:01,120
to the monarch of Liangguo in person.



00:14:01,820 --> 00:14:04,400
I promise him that I’ll cooperate
with him in wiping out Huaiwu.



00:14:04,840 --> 00:14:06,000
With this letter,



00:14:06,420 --> 00:14:08,180
the King of Liangguo will
definitely go out to battle in person.



00:14:08,580 --> 00:14:09,800
You must try every means



00:14:10,380 --> 00:14:12,440
to make sure that
no mistake is made this time.



00:14:16,100 --> 00:14:17,180
I did notice



00:14:17,180 --> 00:14:18,300
the smell of Mu Ci.



00:14:20,300 --> 00:14:20,960
Yes.



00:14:22,420 --> 00:14:24,060
Once the monarch of Liangguo
goes out to battle in person,



00:14:24,440 --> 00:14:26,060
Xu Feng will accept battle in person too.



00:14:26,540 --> 00:14:28,280
When he leaves Beiyuan Villa,



00:14:28,840 --> 00:14:30,280
you have to kill Jin Mi for me.



00:14:33,260 --> 00:14:35,060
It turns out that his target is Jin Mi.



00:14:35,220 --> 00:14:36,880
Even without Spirit-Vanishing Arrow,



00:14:37,460 --> 00:14:39,640
you should send her back to Heaven Realm
to restart experiencing hardships.



00:14:40,260 --> 00:14:41,440
I can hardly wait.



00:14:41,500 --> 00:14:42,360
Wait, Your Highness.



00:14:42,820 --> 00:14:44,380
Her Majesty ordered me



00:14:44,960 --> 00:14:46,380
to recover Spirit-Vanishing Arrow first.



00:14:46,940 --> 00:14:47,900
She worries that



00:14:48,060 --> 00:14:49,300
someone may harm the second Prince



00:14:49,360 --> 00:14:50,640
with this arrow.



00:14:50,640 --> 00:14:53,740
So does she know your arrangement?



00:14:54,520 --> 00:14:55,540
In this case,



00:14:56,380 --> 00:14:57,860
after sending the letter,



00:14:58,060 --> 00:14:59,260
go to protect Xu Feng.



00:14:59,460 --> 00:15:01,720
If anyone wants to hurt him
with Spirit-Vanishing Arrow,



00:15:02,060 --> 00:15:03,820
you can take the chance to take the arrow



00:15:04,060 --> 00:15:05,280
to kill Jin Mi.



00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:07,280
Yes.



00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:19,300
It turns out that you left
without saying a word that day



00:15:19,580 --> 00:15:21,300
was to kill Jin Mi.



00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:22,860
She is my friend.



00:15:22,980 --> 00:15:24,520
I won’t allow you to hurt her.



00:15:27,320 --> 00:15:29,800
Mu Ci, what has happened
to you all these years?



00:15:29,860 --> 00:15:31,420
Why do you want to kill her?



00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:33,960
If you have any trouble, you can tell me.



00:15:34,360 --> 00:15:35,320
I’ll help you.



00:15:40,020 --> 00:15:41,180
If you insist on killing her,



00:15:41,360 --> 00:15:42,440
you are my enemy.



00:15:53,940 --> 00:15:54,960
That’s better.



00:16:29,260 --> 00:16:31,180
Why is there the smell
of my bones and blood here?



00:16:50,840 --> 00:16:51,680
Luckily,



00:16:52,100 --> 00:16:53,520
Spirit-Vanishing Arrow is hanging here,



00:16:53,800 --> 00:16:55,340
but it doesn’t hurt the second Princess.



00:16:57,700 --> 00:17:00,360
Jin Mi, I’m sorry.



00:17:00,540 --> 00:17:01,940
It’s my fault.



00:17:03,800 --> 00:17:04,660
Jin Mi.



00:17:08,280 --> 00:17:09,619
You must be crazy



00:17:09,940 --> 00:17:11,800
to take three tablets of Wu Yin.



00:17:13,220 --> 00:17:15,040
Only it can suppress



00:17:16,500 --> 00:17:18,140
the syndrome of Qing Yue.



00:17:18,140 --> 00:17:20,020
But it’s also poisonous.



00:17:20,480 --> 00:17:23,400
Taking such a deadly poison, you’ll die.



00:17:24,119 --> 00:17:26,339
I have only some time to stay with him.



00:17:28,760 --> 00:17:31,040
I don’t want him to see my sickly look



00:17:32,300 --> 00:17:34,260
and worry about me



00:17:36,040 --> 00:17:37,640
when he is with me.



00:17:41,020 --> 00:17:41,800
In the past,



00:17:42,180 --> 00:17:44,800
I thought you were
the smartest person in the world,



00:17:45,520 --> 00:17:46,800
but now to me



00:17:46,880 --> 00:17:49,060
you’re totally a fool.



00:17:54,520 --> 00:17:55,240
Jin Mi.



00:17:57,000 --> 00:17:57,620
Jin Mi.



00:17:59,480 --> 00:18:00,160
Jin Mi.



00:18:07,580 --> 00:18:08,680
Your Majesty.



00:18:09,940 --> 00:18:10,860
Your Majesty,



00:18:11,540 --> 00:18:13,160
Saint Girl is getting changed.



00:18:13,220 --> 00:18:15,140
Please wait for a while in the courtyard.



00:18:16,300 --> 00:18:17,140
OK.



00:18:39,540 --> 00:18:40,320
Your Majesty,



00:18:49,140 --> 00:18:50,520
you’re going to the front line again.



00:18:51,680 --> 00:18:53,180
Originally, I thought
after we defeated Liangguo,



00:18:53,360 --> 00:18:55,180
they would take no action in a short time.



00:18:55,980 --> 00:18:57,180
However, it’s out of expectation that



00:18:57,360 --> 00:18:59,580
the King of Liangguo will fight personally,



00:19:01,300 --> 00:19:04,560
so I have to accept battle again.



00:19:05,640 --> 00:19:06,560
Your Majesty,



00:19:08,080 --> 00:19:08,960
I…



00:19:09,700 --> 00:19:11,460
I’m afraid I can’t wait for you.



00:19:11,920 --> 00:19:14,880
What? You can’t wait for these few days?



00:19:21,280 --> 00:19:22,240
Originally, I thought



00:19:22,880 --> 00:19:24,240
as you were so stubborn before,



00:19:24,640 --> 00:19:26,240
we had to wait for all this life.



00:19:26,400 --> 00:19:27,740
I thought the happiest time in my life



00:19:27,740 --> 00:19:28,840
would come after we died



00:19:28,840 --> 00:19:31,140
and were buried
in the emperor’s tomb together.



00:19:31,640 --> 00:19:32,680
But now



00:19:33,260 --> 00:19:34,440
you’re willing to wait for me



00:19:34,620 --> 00:19:36,100
and create future with me.



00:19:36,660 --> 00:19:39,360
Happiness comes so fast



00:19:39,640 --> 00:19:40,860
that it’s like a dream.



00:19:43,320 --> 00:19:44,120
Jin Mi,



00:19:45,420 --> 00:19:47,360
do you really want to be with me



00:19:47,940 --> 00:19:49,160
and be my queen forever?



00:19:59,960 --> 00:20:00,900
I do.



00:20:03,200 --> 00:20:05,020
But how about your promise to the people?



00:20:05,260 --> 00:20:06,900
You said you won’t get married



00:20:08,140 --> 00:20:09,360
before unifying the state.



00:20:10,500 --> 00:20:12,880
This is just nonsense.



00:20:13,480 --> 00:20:15,440
It was just because
you were so stubborn back then



00:20:15,560 --> 00:20:17,060
that I used it as an excuse



00:20:17,220 --> 00:20:18,420
to refuse the officials.



00:20:19,020 --> 00:20:20,080
But I really want to



00:20:20,420 --> 00:20:22,080
declare to the world



00:20:22,640 --> 00:20:24,080
and let everyone know



00:20:24,560 --> 00:20:25,860
you’re my queen now.



00:20:32,560 --> 00:20:33,940
Since I’ve promised you,



00:20:34,820 --> 00:20:36,400
I’ll always wait for you here.



00:20:38,940 --> 00:20:41,860
Aren’t you going to make a plan



00:20:42,120 --> 00:20:44,140
to help me get rid of the status of Saint Girl?



00:20:45,240 --> 00:20:46,540
We have a whole life,



00:20:47,600 --> 00:20:48,640
so don’t be hasty now.



00:20:51,400 --> 00:20:52,760
But...



00:20:53,000 --> 00:20:54,160
What?



00:20:54,960 --> 00:20:56,160
It’ll be your greatest honor



00:20:56,760 --> 00:20:58,160
to marry me as your queen.



00:20:59,200 --> 00:21:00,920
Don’t think of taking consorts afterwards.



00:21:01,560 --> 00:21:04,060
You can’t even take a look at other girls.



00:21:04,280 --> 00:21:05,060
You know?



00:21:06,980 --> 00:21:08,620
Of course, this is my greatest honor.



00:21:09,080 --> 00:21:11,000
I’m unwilling to turn my eyes away from you.



00:21:12,120 --> 00:21:13,300
However, you haven’t seen



00:21:13,300 --> 00:21:14,520
my face until now.



00:21:15,280 --> 00:21:16,980
How do you know
that you won’t turn your eyes away?



00:21:17,080 --> 00:21:18,980
What if I am ugly and you regret?



00:21:20,820 --> 00:21:21,760
How about



00:21:23,260 --> 00:21:24,220
taking it off now?



00:21:24,220 --> 00:21:24,700
No need.



00:21:26,700 --> 00:21:28,000
Even if you’re ugly,



00:21:28,460 --> 00:21:30,220
don’t try to escape from me.



00:21:30,880 --> 00:21:32,500
You don’t have to take off the veil now.



00:21:33,160 --> 00:21:34,600
On our wedding night,



